<!doctype html><html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1"><title>Ed Hatrick Smith - Heatwell project</title><meta name="description" content="Ed Hatrick-Smith: Heatwell project "/><meta name="keywords" content="web developer, desginer, photographer, awesome person, solutions"/><meta name="author" content="Edward Hatrick-Smith: ed.hatricksmith@gmail.com"/><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styles.projects.min.css"/><?php $thisPage="work";?><?php include_once("/home/akolob/public_html/analyticstracking.php") ?></head><body><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/header.php");?><div id="projects"><h1 class="works_heading">Heatwell</h1><p class="breadcrumbs"><em><a href="/work/work.php">Work</a> / Heatwell</em></p><article><p class="projects_first">Heatwell is a local under floor heating company owned by my friend's Dad. He's a good sort and needed not only a redesign of his somewhat dated website but also some good, useful advice on how he could improve his <span class="small-cap">s.e.o.</span> as well as some basic marketing strategies. He also wanted to be able to make changes to the content himself.</p><p>I kept the design very clean and professional but still with some warmth of colour here and there. We went with a <span class="small-cap">cms</span> solution called <a href="http://unify.unitinteractive.com/" target="_blank">Unify</a>. It's rather basic but allows the user to edit text and pictures - which was perfect for him. It was also incredibly easy and therefore cheap to implement.</p><p>He's now also keeping a sharp eye on his analytics as well as actively engaging in Google AdWords campaigns.</p></article><section><h2 class="works_heading">Project Images</h2><div id="container" class="project_width"><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/heatwell/image_01_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/heatwell/image_01_sml.jpg" alt="Heatwell home page"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/heatwell/image_02_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/heatwell/image_02_sml.jpg" alt="Heatwell heating options"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a><a class="fancybox gallery" href="/images/works/projects/heatwell/image_03_lge.jpg"><div class="project project_sm"><img src="/images/works/projects/heatwell/image_03_sml.jpg" alt="Heatwell page detail 01"><div class="caption fade-caption"><h3 class="element_title">Enlarge</h3></div></div></a></div><div class="clearfix"></div></section><ul><li><a href="http://www.heatwell.co.nz/" target="_blank">Visit Website</a></li></ul></div><div class="clearfix"></div><?php include("/home/akolob/public_html/footer.php");?><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.projects.min.js" ></script><script type="text/javascript">$(".fancybox") .attr('rel', 'gallery') .fancybox({padding : 0 ,minWidth : 215 ,maxWidth : 900 ,autoSize : true ,maxHeight : 600 ,});</script><script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.0/jquery.min.js"></script><script src="/js/jquery.isotope-min.js"></script><script type="text/javascript">$(function(){var $container=$('#container');$container.isotope({itemSelector: '.project'});});</script></body></html>